ttps://second.com\nSession restored with 2 history entries, current URL: https://first.com"}, {"input": "navigate url=https://fresh.com\nrestore_session", "description": "Attempt to restore session when no state was saved", "expected_output": "Navigated to https://fresh.com, history saved\nNo session state to restore."}, {"input": "navigate url=https://v1.com\nsave_session\nnavigate url=https://v2.com\nnavigate url=https://v3.com\nsave_session\nnavigate url=https://v4.com\nrestore_session", "description": "Save multiple sessions, verify last one is restored", "expected_output": "Navigated to https://v1.com, history saved\nSession state saved.\nNavigated to https://v2.com, history saved\nNavigated to https://v3.com, history saved\nSession state saved.\nNavigated to https://v4.com, history saved\nSession restored with 3 history entries, current URL: https://v3.com"}]'::jsonb
