cription": "Check for a drug interaction that should return a warning", "expected_output": "Warning: Warfarin and Aspirin increase bleeding risk."}, {"input": "add_prescription patient=P005, drug=Simvastatin, dosage=20mg\ndispense prescription=RX001\nrefill prescription=RX001", "description": "Test a full cycle: add a prescription (RX001), dispense it, then refill it", "expected_output": "Prescription added: Simvastatin 20mg for P005\nSimvastatin 20mg dispensed for P005\nPrescription RX001 refilled"}]'::jsonb
