: "Search with no results", "expected_output": "Property listed: 123 Main St, $350,000 condo\n0 results."}, {"input": "list_property address=123 Main St, price=350000, type=condo\nmark_sold property=123 Main St\nmark_sold property=123 Main St", "description": "Marking an already sold property", "expected_output": "Property listed: 123 Main St, $350,000 condo\nProperty 123 Main St marked as sold\nError executing command ''mark_sold'': Property 123 Main St is already sold."}, {"input": "list_property address=123 Main St, price=350000, type=condo\ncontact agent=A001 for property=NonExistentProperty\ncontact agent=B002 for property=123 Main St", "description": "Contacting non-existent property/agent", "expected_output": "Property listed: 123 Main St, $350,000 condo\nError executing command ''contact'': Property NonExistentProperty not found.\nError executing command ''contact'': Agent B002 not found."}, {"input": "list_property address=123 Main St, price=350000, type=condo\nlist_property address=123 Main St, price=400000, type=house", "description": "Attempt to list property with existing address", "expected_output": "Property listed: 123 Main St, $350,000 condo\nError executing command ''list_property'': Property at 123 Main St already exists."}]'::jsonb
