wo appointments, cancel the first, then check availability. The cancelled slot should become available again.", "expected_output": "Appointment booked: alice with Dr. Smith at 09:00\nAppointment booked: bob with Dr. Smith at 10:00\nAppointment APT001 cancelled, slot freed\nDr. Smith 2024-07-10 available: 09:00-10:00, 11:00-12:00"}]'::jsonb
