d_output": "PROD001 added, reorder point set at 10\nAlert: PROD001 at 5 units (below reorder point 10)\nPROD001 quantity updated to 12\nReorder needed: []"}, {"input": "add_item sku=PROD001, qty=5, reorder_point=10\nacknowledge_alert sku=PROD001\nupdate_qty sku=PROD001, qty=8\nget_reorder_list", "description": "Acknowledge alert, then update below reorder again (re-trigger)", "expected_output": "PROD001 added, reorder point set at 10\nAlert: PROD001 at 5 units (below reorder point 10)\nReorder acknowledged for PROD001\nAlert: PROD001 at 8 units (below reorder point 10)\nReorder needed: [PROD001: 8 units]"}]'::jsonb
