ed.\nBooking CAMP001 created for alice at LV_05 from 2024-08-10 to 2024-08-14\nError: Campsite LV_05 is not available from 2024-08-12 to 2024-08-16."}, {"input": "add_campsite id=LV_01, name=Lake_View_01, type=tent\nbook site_id=LV_01, user=alice, dates=2024-08-10 to 2024-08-14\nsearch site_name_contains=Lake_View, dates=2024-08-10 to 2024-08-14, type=tent", "description": "Search reflects booked sites as unavailable", "expected_output": "Campsite LV_01 (Lake_View_01, tent) added.\nBooking CAMP001 created for alice at LV_01 from 2024-08-10 to 2024-08-14\nNo sites found matching criteria."}, {"input": "add_campsite id=LV_05, name=Lake_View_05, type=tent\nbook site_id=LV_05, user=alice, dates=2024-08-10 to 2024-08-14\ncheck_in booking=CAMP001\ncheck_out booking=CAMP001", "description": "Check out from a booked campsite", "expected_output": "Campsite LV_05 (Lake_View_05, tent) added.\nBooking CAMP001 created for alice at LV_05 from 2024-08-10 to 2024-08-14\nalice checked in to site LV_05 for booking CAMP001.\nalice checked out from site LV_05 for booking CAMP001."}]'::jsonb
