tially knows members: [n1, n2, n3].\nNode n3 marked as FAILED.\nStarting 3 global gossip rounds.\nGlobal gossip round completed.\nGlobal gossip round completed.\nGlobal gossip round completed.\n3 global gossip rounds completed.\nCurrent system state:\n  n1: ALIVE, members=[n1, n2, n3, n4].\n  n2: ALIVE, members=[n1, n2, n3, n4].\n  n3: FAILED, members=[n1, n2, n3, n4].\n  n4: ALIVE, members=[n1, n2, n3, n4]."}]'::jsonb
