solation=snapshot\nread TXN002 key=user_4\nwrite TXN002 key=user_4 value=value_B\nread TXN002 key=user_4\ncommit TXN002", "description": "Transaction reads its own writes and subsequent commits", "expected_output": "Transaction TXN001 started with snapshot at version 0\nTXN001 writes user_4 with value value_A\nTXN001 reads user_4 at snapshot version 0 (pending write value: value_A)\nTXN001 committed, new version 1 created\nTransaction TXN002 started with snapshot at version 1\nTXN002 reads user_4 at snapshot version 1 (value: value_A)\nTXN002 writes user_4 with value value_B\nTXN002 reads user_4 at snapshot version 1 (pending write value: value_B)\nTXN002 committed, new version 2 created"}]'::jsonb
