end at invalid (negative) offset", "expected_output": "Event appended to journal at offset 1\nError: duplicate offset rejected, journal is append-only"}, {"input": "APPEND {\"type\": \"Custom\", \"data\": \"some long string data to test payload limits\"}", "description": "Append event with complex data", "expected_output": "Event appended to journal at offset 1"}, {"input": "APPEND {\"type\": \"Initial\"}\nAPPEND {\"type\": \"Second\"}\nAPPEND_AT {\"type\": \"Overwrite\"} 2", "description": "Attempt to overwrite an existing event with APPEND_AT", "expected_output": "Event appended to journal at offset 1\nEvent appended to journal at offset 2\nError: duplicate offset rejected, journal is append-only"}]'::jsonb
